    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You're targeted by a melee attack.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> You have adrenaline and you aren't encumbered.</p><hr /><p>You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the attack. After the attack, you can Stride up to half your Speed. If you do, the attacker can Stride to follow you as a free action, keeping you in their reach throughout their movement until you stop moving or they have moved their full Speed.</p>",
